---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Projects - Anthony Guzzardo" description="Projects built by Anthony Guzzardo" background="frosted">
<main class="page-content">
  <div class="container">


    <div class="projects-grid">
      <div class="project-card-horizontal dealifier-card">
        <img src="/images/dealifier/appIcon.png" alt="Dealifier App Icon" class="project-icon dealifier-icon" />
        <div class="project-info">
          <h3>Dealifier <span class="project-status">Coming Soon</span></h3>
          <p>A location-based marketplace that drops every live local deal onto one map. Consumers filter by category, price, distance, and discount to surface only the offers worth the trip; businesses create deals in seconds and redeem them with QR. Full stack: iOS consumer and business apps, an Astro marketing site, and a Supabase backend with Stripe payments and vector search.</p>
          <a href="https://dealifier.com" target="_blank" class="project-link">
            Visit Site
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card-horizontal sfsg-card">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 120 120" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="project-icon sfsg-icon">
          <rect width="120" height="120" rx="24" fill="#07070a" />
          {/* Wind lines — the rush of the fall */}
          <g stroke="#ffb84d" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.25">
            <line x1="26" y1="30" x2="26" y2="48" />
            <line x1="92" y1="26" x2="92" y2="50" />
            <line x1="38" y1="74" x2="38" y2="92" />
            <line x1="84" y1="78" x2="84" y2="92" />
          </g>
          {/* The falling man — lifted from the atlas hero (viewBox 200x520) */}
          <g fill="#ffb84d" transform="translate(42, 11) scale(0.19)">
            <circle cx="105" cy="42" r="22" />
            <path d="M 95 62 C 90 90, 85 130, 80 170 L 70 170 C 75 130, 80 90, 85 62 Z" />
            <path d="M 85 75 C 60 60, 30 45, 5 55 L 3 48 C 28 35, 58 50, 83 68 Z" />
            <path d="M 95 80 C 120 95, 155 120, 185 105 L 188 112 C 158 130, 122 105, 95 88 Z" />
            <path d="M 80 100 C 75 130, 65 165, 55 195 C 50 205, 58 208, 65 200 C 70 175, 75 145, 80 115 Z" opacity="0.7" />
            <path d="M 72 170 C 65 200, 55 240, 45 260 C 40 268, 48 272, 55 265 C 60 245, 68 210, 74 180 Z" opacity="0.5" />
            <path d="M 78 165 C 70 210, 55 260, 40 310 C 35 330, 25 360, 20 380 L 12 378 C 18 358, 28 328, 33 308 C 48 258, 63 208, 70 168 Z" />
            <path d="M 20 378 L 12 378 C 5 390, 2 400, 8 405 L 22 400 C 25 395, 24 388, 20 380 Z" />
            <path d="M 82 168 C 90 220, 100 290, 110 360 C 115 400, 120 440, 118 470 L 108 468 C 110 438, 107 398, 102 358 C 92 288, 85 220, 76 170 Z" />
            <path d="M 118 468 L 108 468 C 106 480, 108 490, 115 495 L 125 492 C 128 487, 125 478, 118 470 Z" />
          </g>
        </svg>
        <div class="project-info">
          <h3>So Far So Good</h3>
          <p>A living atlas of scientific knowledge, built on one conviction: science doesn't have a knowledge problem, it has an infrastructure problem. It opens on 188 of NASA's wildest funded concepts and grows into connective tissue for the whole field. A queryable graph of claims and evidence. A graveyard of negative results. Curated reading paths. And Pulse, a live Bloomberg-style board of what space and science are talking about right now. The name is the falling man's mantra from <em>La Haine</em>: <span class="sfsg-mantra">jusqu'ici tout va bien</span>. The journey is the point.</p>
          <a href="https://hactenusbene.com" target="_blank" class="project-link">
            Enter the atlas
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card-horizontal alice-card">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 120 120" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="project-icon alice-icon">
          <rect width="120" height="120" rx="24" fill="#f5f2ed" />
          <g stroke="#7a5a44" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.4">
            <line x1="40" y1="44" x2="62" y2="34" />
            <line x1="62" y1="34" x2="82" y2="52" />
            <line x1="40" y1="44" x2="52" y2="70" />
            <line x1="52" y1="70" x2="82" y2="52" />
            <line x1="52" y1="70" x2="74" y2="84" />
          </g>
          <g fill="#7a5a44">
            <circle cx="40" cy="44" r="3" />
            <circle cx="62" cy="34" r="2.5" />
            <circle cx="82" cy="52" r="3" />
            <circle cx="52" cy="70" r="2.5" />
            <circle cx="74" cy="84" r="3.5" />
          </g>
        </svg>
        <div class="project-info">
          <h3>Alice <span class="project-status">In Development</span></h3>
          <p>A monastic daily journal designed as a longitudinal self-study. Deep journal sessions and calibration sessions establish a baseline and recognize patterns over years. Zero gamification. Largely a black box, not meant to gratify.</p>
          <a href="https://fweeo.com/showcase" target="_blank" class="project-link">
            Enter Alice
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card-horizontal rangley-card">
        <img src="/images/PigSticker.png" alt="Rangley App Icon" class="project-icon rangley-icon" />
        <div class="project-info">
          <h3>Rangley <span class="project-status">Shut Down</span></h3>
          <p>A location-based social meetup app that was built for iOS. End-to-end: SwiftUI frontend, Vapor backend, AWS deployment. Servers were shut down in March 2026.</p>
          <a href="/rangley" class="project-link">
            Read More
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</main>

<style is:global>
  /* Give the first card clearance from the fixed navbar so it isn't
     riding up tight against it. */
  .projects-grid {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  /* Alice card: a window into Alice's own aesthetic, not the portfolio
     boilerplate. Cream "monastic" palette + Cormorant / EB Garamond serif,
     lifted straight from the Alice design tokens. Reads as a quiet island
     against the dark portfolio cards. */
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@1,300;1,400;1,500&family=EB+Garamond:ital@0;1&display=swap');

  .project-card-horizontal.alice-card {
    background: #f5f2ed;
    border: 1px solid #ccc5bc;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(40, 30, 20, 0.12);
  }
  .project-card-horizontal.alice-card:hover {
    background: #f0ece4;
    border-color: #8a8580;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(40, 30, 20, 0.18);
  }

  .alice-card .project-icon.alice-icon {
    box-shadow: none;
    border: 1px solid #e0dbd5;
    background: #f5f2ed;
  }

  .alice-card .project-info h3 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .alice-card .project-info p {
    font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    color: #6b6560;
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .alice-card .project-status {
    background: #e0dbd5;
    color: #6b6560;
    font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', monospace;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .alice-card .project-link {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #7a5a44;
  }
  .alice-card .project-link:hover { color: #1a1a1a; }

  /* So Far So Good card: a window into the atlas's own aesthetic, not the
     portfolio boilerplate. Deep-space paper (#07070a), amber accent
     (#ffb84d), and a serif display face — the exact design tokens from the
     site. Rauschenberg-meets-JPL, a Bloomberg terminal for space nerds. */
  .project-card-horizontal.sfsg-card {
    background:
      radial-gradient(140% 120% at 18% 0%, rgba(255, 184, 77, 0.10) 0%, transparent 55%),
      #07070a;
    border: 1px solid #25252d;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
  }
  .project-card-horizontal.sfsg-card:hover {
    border-color: #8a5a1c;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), 0 0 32px rgba(255, 184, 77, 0.10);
  }

  .sfsg-card .project-icon.sfsg-icon {
    border: 1px solid #25252d;
    background: #07070a;
    box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(255, 184, 77, 0.12);
  }

  .sfsg-card .project-info h3 {
    font-family: ui-serif, 'Iowan Old Style', 'Apple Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #e8e6df;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .sfsg-card .project-info p {
    color: #9a978c;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .sfsg-card .project-info p em {
    color: #c8c5bc;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .sfsg-card .sfsg-mantra {
    font-family: ui-serif, 'Iowan Old Style', 'Apple Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #ffb84d;
  }

  .sfsg-card .project-link {
    font-family: ui-serif, 'Iowan Old Style', 'Apple Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    color: #ffb84d;
  }
  .sfsg-card .project-link:hover { color: #e8e6df; }

  /* Rangley card: a window into the app's own aesthetic — dark Japanese
     purple surface (japDarkerPurple #3C177B), neon-pink accent (#FF007D),
     white text hierarchy. A solid, opaque surface so copy stays readable
     instead of the site background bleeding through. */
  .project-card-horizontal.rangley-card {
    background:
      radial-gradient(120% 140% at 12% 0%, rgba(255, 0, 125, 0.16) 0%, transparent 55%),
      #3C177B;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
  }
  .project-card-horizontal.rangley-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255, 0, 125, 0.5);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55), 0 0 34px rgba(255, 0, 125, 0.28);
  }

  .rangley-card .project-icon.rangley-icon {
    border-radius: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), 0 0 28px rgba(255, 0, 125, 0.3);
  }

  .rangley-card .project-info h3 {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .rangley-card .project-info p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
  }

  /* Neon-pink pill badge — replaces the grey global default */
  .rangley-card .project-status {
    background: rgba(255, 0, 125, 0.14);
    color: #FF007D;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 0, 125, 0.5);
    border-radius: 999px;
    opacity: 1;
    box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(255, 0, 125, 0.25);
  }

  .rangley-card .project-link {
    color: #FF007D;
  }
  .rangley-card .project-link:hover { color: #ffffff; }

  /* Dealifier card: a window into the app's own aesthetic — Dealifier's
     brand red (#C42224, light #FF5252) on a clean near-black surface,
     lifted straight from the app's design tokens. Minimal, no decorative
     shapes, a quiet red glow to echo the price-tag pin. */
  .project-card-horizontal.dealifier-card {
    background:
      radial-gradient(120% 140% at 12% 0%, rgba(255, 82, 82, 0.14) 0%, transparent 55%),
      #14161b;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.10);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
  }
  .project-card-horizontal.dealifier-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255, 82, 82, 0.5);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55), 0 0 34px rgba(196, 34, 36, 0.3);
  }

  .dealifier-card .project-icon.dealifier-icon {
    /* The PNG already carries its own rounded black border, so let it show
       in full (contain, no extra radius) instead of clipping the corners. */
    border-radius: 0;
    object-fit: contain;
    box-shadow: none;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4)) drop-shadow(0 0 22px rgba(196, 34, 36, 0.28));
  }

  .dealifier-card .project-info h3 {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .dealifier-card .project-info p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
  }

  /* Brand-red pill badge — replaces the grey global default */
  .dealifier-card .project-status {
    background: rgba(196, 34, 36, 0.16);
    color: #FF5252;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 82, 82, 0.5);
    border-radius: 999px;
    opacity: 1;
    box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(196, 34, 36, 0.25);
  }

  .dealifier-card .project-link {
    color: #FF5252;
  }
  .dealifier-card .project-link:hover { color: #ffffff; }
</style>
</Layout>
